with everything I can muster.

332
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:10,000
[squeals]

333
00:18:10,083 --> 00:18:12,208
I do look forward
to it very much.

334
00:18:12,291 --> 00:18:13,916
Welcome to the family, son.

335
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,375
[KIMITO] I don't want
her to be my mommy!

336
00:18:16,458 --> 00:18:18,041
[AIKA]
Hold on a second, lady!

337
00:18:18,125 --> 00:18:20,166
Objection!

338
00:18:20,250 --> 00:18:22,333
We invoke our three fifths
majority in the Commoner Club

339
00:18:22,416 --> 00:18:23,708
to veto this marriage!

340
00:18:23,791 --> 00:18:25,250
That's right!

341
00:18:25,333 --> 00:18:27,625
