344
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,333
No, it's not!

345
00:18:34,875 --> 00:18:36,416
You have got some nerve!

346
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:37,875
How dare you dodge
my sucker punch!

347
00:18:37,958 --> 00:18:38,916
What am I supposed to do,

348
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:40,708
