350
00:18:42,333 --> 00:18:44,500
That's why I'm taking
you out, pervert!

351
00:18:44,583 --> 00:18:46,125
[yelping]

352
00:18:46,208 --> 00:18:48,416
[MASAOMI] Reiko's my
little sister, not yours!

353
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:50,583
I never said she was,
you big weirdo!

354
00:18:50,666 --> 00:18:51,708
[growls]

355
00:18:51,791 --> 00:18:52,875
Time to die!

356
00:18:52,958 --> 00:18:54,750
[KIMITO]
Reiko! Can't you stop him?

357
00:18:54,833 --> 00:18:57,250
[REIKO]
"One hundred Fun Wedding Ideas."

358
00:18:57,333 --> 00:18:58,916
