engrossing literature!

360
00:19:00,833 --> 00:19:02,833
You have no cause to be
reading that, ya hear?

361
00:19:02,916 --> 00:19:04,416
We should confiscate it.

362
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,208
[REIKO]
Ah!

363
00:19:05,291 --> 00:19:06,750
