to stop you from leaving?

365
00:19:09,833 --> 00:19:12,458
Obviously, I will come
visit you whenever I can!

366
00:19:12,541 --> 00:19:15,291
I don't really care if I ever
see your treacherous face again.

367
00:19:15,375 --> 00:19:17,500
[KIMITO] Your brother's
a friggin' psycho!

368
00:19:17,583 --> 00:19:20,041
